Set the camera in the middle of the coater. Will fixed
Crop out each controllers, make sure to include all the corners. It's ok to include a corner from the next controller
Adjust the exposure time. Make sure all the digits are captured. Longer than the electronic flink time
The exposure time can't be too long. After cropping the controller, check the average of its h and s channel.
The h_ave and s_ave should be both > 70 (longer exposure, brighter image, lower value) to use the s channel.